Show config paths, OpenCode availability, and integration status

Usage: doctor [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --install-missing
          Install missing OpenCode 2, tokei, and Universal Ctags with global mise config

      --check
          Validate the effective oy agent, commands, skills, and models; exit nonzero on failure

